<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <p>Mo' Mondays Mo' Problems!</p>
    ===============================================
    <h2>THE EVENT IS SET!</h2>

    <p>
      Voting has just finished for <%="'#{@event.name}' created by #{@event.user}" %>. Below is the event information: <br/>
    </p>
    <p>
      <b>Event Name:</b> "<%= @event.name %>" <br/>
      <b>Event Start Time:</b> <%= @event.event_start.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %> at <%= @event.event_start.strftime("%I:%M%p") %><br/>
      <b>Winning Venue:</b> "<%= @winner.name %>" suggested by <%= @winner.user.username %><br/>
      <b>Address Info:</b> <br/> <%= @winner.address.html_safe %> <br/>
      <% if !@winner.url.blank? %>
        <b>Venue URL: </b><%= @winner.url %> <br/>
      <% end %>
      <% if !@event.notes.blank? %>
        <b>Notes to Guests:</b> <br/>
        "<%= @event.notes %> "
      <% end %>
    </p>
     
    <p>Are you going? RSVP using the discussion box on the <%= link_to("Event Page", @url) %></p>

    <p>Hope to see you there!</p>
    <p>-Mo' Mondays App</p>
     ===============================================
  </body>
</html>